<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10281265>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Valeriana dacica Porcius. General habit (left: lectotype, BP; right: probable syntype, CL). Note the broadly ovate or round middle leaflet of cauline leaves." ;
